Hi there! I'm here to help. Could you please let me know what specific issue or question you have? I'll do my best to assist you right away.
I was invited to this account and I have employee role, how do I remove myself to this account?

To remove yourself from an account where you have an employee role, you'll need to contact the account administrator or owner. They can change your role or remove you from the account. If you need further assistance, feel free to reach out!
how about the billing ? do i need to create a new one

Yes, billing is separate for each ad account. If you're creating a new ad account, you'll need to set up a new billing method for it. Each account requires its own billing setup. If you have any more questions about this, feel free to ask!
